WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.070
Hey, good morning family. How are y'all

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:06.030
doing today? I'm going to do a video

00:00:06.030 --> 00:00:06.040
on

00:00:06.040 --> 00:00:07.789
some things that are on my heart

00:00:07.799 --> 00:00:09.870
that I've been praying over.

00:00:09.880 --> 00:00:11.470
We are really close to the

00:00:11.480 --> 00:00:14.990
Fourth of July weekend,

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.550
basically next weekend, and

00:00:17.550 --> 00:00:17.560
I am

00:00:17.560 --> 00:00:20.230
interceding for protection for your

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:23.230
families and for where you're at,

00:00:23.240 --> 00:00:25.109
watching your surroundings. The

00:00:25.119 --> 00:00:26.630
Lord just had it on my heart again to

00:00:26.630 --> 00:00:26.640
pray

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:29.990
that there are no

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.270
terrorist activities during this

00:00:32.270 --> 00:00:32.280
timeframe.

00:00:32.280 --> 00:00:35.830
Like I said, it was heavy on

00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:37.630
me last night, and I was interceding for

00:00:37.640 --> 00:00:39.830
the nation and for people's

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:42.229
safety in general at public

00:00:42.239 --> 00:00:44.790
gatherings and things like that.

00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:48.069
I made a video a while back

00:00:48.079 --> 00:00:49.590
about praying for your children when

00:00:49.600 --> 00:00:51.750
they go back to school and making a

00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:54.990
bloodline of protection for them

00:00:54.990 --> 00:00:55.000
so that

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:57.389
no

00:00:57.399 --> 00:00:59.470
calamity would come nigh them when they

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:02.270
go to school or wherever. I'm

00:01:02.280 --> 00:01:04.549
going to play that video again here in a

00:01:04.559 --> 00:01:05.830
couple of seconds if you want to watch

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:08.310
it.

00:01:08.320 --> 00:01:10.429
I'm not

00:01:10.439 --> 00:01:13.590
used to filming in the car, but

00:01:13.600 --> 00:01:16.950
making a public hedge of

00:01:16.960 --> 00:01:19.510
protection over your churches and praying

00:01:19.520 --> 00:01:23.550
over

00:01:23.560 --> 00:01:26.270
places that you're

00:01:26.280 --> 00:01:28.590
going... this is

00:01:28.600 --> 00:01:31.670
a very serious

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:35.710
time, a time that we need to be very

00:01:35.720 --> 00:01:38.870
vigilant and watchful of where we are at

00:01:38.880 --> 00:01:41.469
all times. If the Lord speaks to you,

00:01:43.840 --> 00:01:44.830
a lot of times people say, 'Well, I don't

00:01:44.840 --> 00:01:46.350
hear the voice of the Lord.'This is where

00:01:46.360 --> 00:01:48.709
I would go: if you don't have

00:01:48.719 --> 00:01:51.670
peace, then don't go. If you feel

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:53.550
tormented or bothered,

00:01:53.560 --> 00:01:55.670
the Lord is not a God

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:57.830
of torment, but he is a God of warning,

00:01:57.840 --> 00:02:00.230
and he warns us in our spirits. He would

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:03.469
say, 'I don't want you to go to that

00:02:05.550 --> 00:02:05.560
place,'and

00:02:07.600 --> 00:02:09.790
you have to listen. You have to

00:02:09.800 --> 00:02:13.070
be sensitive to the Spirit of God every

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:15.670
single day regarding where you're supposed to

00:02:15.670 --> 00:02:15.680
be—the

00:02:15.680 --> 00:02:18.030
grocery store, the

00:02:18.040 --> 00:02:20.430
gas station, whatever. He may say, 'Don't go

00:02:20.440 --> 00:02:21.869
down that street right there that you're

00:02:21.879 --> 00:02:24.270
fixing to go down; go down the next one.'You

00:02:24.270 --> 00:02:24.280
might not

00:02:24.280 --> 00:02:26.309
understand

00:02:26.319 --> 00:02:28.949
why, but just follow the voice and

00:02:28.959 --> 00:02:30.830
leading of the Spirit of God inside of

00:02:30.840 --> 00:02:33.190
you at all times. It may not make

00:02:33.200 --> 00:02:36.190
sense to you; it doesn't have to. A lot of

00:02:36.200 --> 00:02:38.430
times when I'm listening to the Lord,

00:02:38.440 --> 00:02:41.350
it's just blind obedience: 'Yes,

00:02:41.360 --> 00:02:43.910
Lord, I will do what you've

00:02:43.920 --> 00:02:47.309
asked me to

00:02:47.309 --> 00:02:47.319
do.'That's

00:02:47.319 --> 00:02:49.589
where we have to

00:02:49.599 --> 00:02:52.550
be in these last days, just trusting

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:54.390
confidently in the finished work of the

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:56.190
Lord and knowing that he's going to

00:02:56.200 --> 00:02:58.350
protect us. He said that he

00:02:58.360 --> 00:03:01.589
would send his angels to bear us up lest

00:03:01.599 --> 00:03:04.990
we dash our foot against a stone.

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:09.630
We claim Psalm 91 and Psalm 23,

00:03:09.640 --> 00:03:12.430
and we believe by faith

00:03:12.440 --> 00:03:14.229
that no weapon

00:03:14.239 --> 00:03:16.309
formed against you or your family would

00:03:16.319 --> 00:03:18.710
prosper. That's where I go every

00:03:18.720 --> 00:03:21.949
single day. I plead the blood of Jesus

00:03:21.949 --> 00:03:21.959
for

00:03:21.959 --> 00:03:24.869
protection and I say, 'Lord, I thank you

00:03:24.879 --> 00:03:26.430
that you said in your word that you

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:28.589
would protect my wife, my children,

00:03:28.599 --> 00:03:30.869
and my loved ones, that you

00:03:30.879 --> 00:03:33.110
have a hedge of protection around

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:35.390
and about us, that your angels keep

00:03:35.400 --> 00:03:37.509
charge over us and they will bear us up

00:03:37.519 --> 00:03:40.229
in their hands lest we dash our foot

00:03:40.239 --> 00:03:41.750
against a

00:03:41.750 --> 00:03:41.760
stone.'Now,

00:03:41.760 --> 00:03:45.429
I believe I receive your

00:03:45.439 --> 00:03:47.869
divine protection over me, my wife,

00:03:47.879 --> 00:03:50.070
and my kids today. I thank you, Lord,

00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:53.069
that I will hear your voice and

00:03:53.079 --> 00:03:55.750
a stranger's voice we will not follow. I

00:03:55.760 --> 00:03:57.830
will not be tormented by a demonic

00:03:57.840 --> 00:04:00.190
spirit; I will not be tormented by

00:04:00.190 --> 00:04:00.200
forebodings

00:04:00.200 --> 00:04:02.910
because sometimes a spirit of forebodings

00:04:02.910 --> 00:04:02.920
comes

00:04:02.920 --> 00:04:04.949
because we hear so much in

00:04:04.959 --> 00:04:07.509
the news

00:04:07.509 --> 00:04:07.519
or

00:04:07.519 --> 00:04:10.030
on

00:04:10.040 --> 00:04:12.470
social

00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:15.990
media, and all of a sudden you will

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:18.629
start to meditate on the wrong thing.

00:04:18.639 --> 00:04:20.270
Because you're thinking on the

00:04:20.280 --> 00:04:21.710
wrong thing, you'll start feeling

00:04:21.720 --> 00:04:23.350
something inside; what you feel is your

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:24.790
spirit, but a lot of times it's just

00:04:24.790 --> 00:04:24.800
flesh—it's

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:27.189
just fear. We have to

00:04:27.199 --> 00:04:29.029
decipher between the Spirit of God

00:04:29.039 --> 00:04:31.430
leading us versus our flesh being in

00:04:31.440 --> 00:04:34.710
fear. That is growing in maturity as a believer. I believe a lot of

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:51.629
times the Lord will

00:04:51.639 --> 00:04:56.230
lead you in peace that

00:04:56.240 --> 00:04:58.550
passes all understanding.

00:04:58.560 --> 00:05:00.909
It's an

00:05:00.919 --> 00:05:03.830
inward knowing: 'I do not need to go there;

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:06.510
I need to go to this other

00:05:06.520 --> 00:05:08.950
store.'I

00:05:08.960 --> 00:05:10.310
feel like

00:05:10.320 --> 00:05:12.710
it's important in these days to really

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:16.990
emphasize the importance of

00:05:20.479 --> 00:05:23.390
listening to the voice of the Lord

00:05:23.390 --> 00:05:23.400
and

00:05:23.400 --> 00:05:25.510
being at the right place at

00:05:25.520 --> 00:05:27.710
the right time. I say that all the time:

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:30.070
I'm always in the right place at the

00:05:30.080 --> 00:05:33.070
right time.

00:05:33.080 --> 00:05:35.909
I will hear my Father's

00:05:35.919 --> 00:05:38.590
voice and I will

00:05:38.600 --> 00:05:42.390
not hear a stranger's voice.

00:05:44.919 --> 00:05:47.870
Father,

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:50.670
I thank you

00:05:50.670 --> 00:05:50.680
that

00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:53.550
you are our God, and

00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:56.790
as for me and my house, we will

00:05:56.800 --> 00:05:58.990
serve the Lord. That's where you have

00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:01.790
to be with that bulldog faith.

00:06:09.680 --> 00:06:12.749
I'm praying for protection

00:06:12.759 --> 00:06:15.230
for the Fourth of July and

00:06:15.230 --> 00:06:15.240
for

00:06:15.240 --> 00:06:17.950
Donald, that he

00:06:17.960 --> 00:06:21.710
would be sheltered and protected, that

00:06:21.720 --> 00:06:26.150
no calamity comes nigh him. I pray that the

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:30.150
enemy's plans would not

00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:31.990
bear any fruit;

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:34.110
they will not bear fruit in what

00:06:34.120 --> 00:06:35.749
they have planned to try to take his

00:06:35.759 --> 00:06:37.990
life. He will always be

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:40.189
protected and

00:06:40.199 --> 00:06:42.670
fulfill what God has called him to do.

00:06:47.160 --> 00:06:49.070
We will have godly leadership back

00:06:49.080 --> 00:06:53.710
in our nation—people that will lead

00:06:53.720 --> 00:06:56.550
and take the United States to where it

00:06:56.560 --> 00:07:00.629
needs to be in these end times.

00:07:00.629 --> 00:07:00.639
I

00:07:00.639 --> 00:07:02.150
want to encourage you all

00:07:02.160 --> 00:07:04.309
today: don't give up on what you're

00:07:04.319 --> 00:07:07.350
believing for. Believe God for

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:10.189
the impossible. Believe

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:18.869
for supernatural increase in

00:07:18.879 --> 00:07:20.629
your life. My wife and I pray for

00:07:20.629 --> 00:07:20.639
peace over your homes and marriages and

00:07:20.639 --> 00:07:22.670
for supernatural increase

00:07:27.469 --> 00:07:27.479
in

00:07:32.160 --> 00:07:34.749
your finances. We believe in the power of

00:07:34.749 --> 00:07:34.759
sowing and reaping.

00:07:34.759 --> 00:07:36.990
We believe

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:46.270
that God is not mocked;

00:07:46.280 --> 00:07:48.589
whatsoever a man soweth, that shall he also

00:07:48.599 --> 00:07:52.430
reap. When you

00:07:52.430 --> 00:07:52.440
sow

00:07:52.440 --> 00:07:55.230
in good soil, you'll reap back thirty, sixty, and a hundredfold. We were tithers, but we used to be 'tippers'—giving sporadically. We saw some

00:08:06.159 --> 00:08:09.629
increase,

00:08:18.599 --> 00:08:21.510
but we never saw real increase until we

00:08:21.510 --> 00:08:21.520
started

00:08:21.520 --> 00:08:25.430
tithing on a regular basis.

00:08:25.440 --> 00:08:27.550
We started

00:08:27.560 --> 00:08:29.510
working for a

00:08:29.520 --> 00:08:34.670
church where it was required by

00:08:34.680 --> 00:08:37.070
being on staff.

00:08:45.920 --> 00:08:49.350
If the pastor there hadn't

00:08:49.350 --> 00:08:49.360
forced

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:51.030
us, we

00:08:51.040 --> 00:08:52.910
never would have been where the

00:08:52.920 --> 00:08:55.829
Lord has taken us now. Believing for

00:08:58.279 --> 00:09:00.389
creative ideas to get

00:09:00.399 --> 00:09:03.870
wealth and believing that God,

00:09:03.870 --> 00:09:03.880
in

00:09:03.880 --> 00:09:06.430
Malachi, rebukes the devourer for our

00:09:06.430 --> 00:09:06.440
sake—that

00:09:06.440 --> 00:09:10.430
was sown deep

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:11.949
inside of

00:09:11.959 --> 00:09:14.670
us. We worked there for 13 years, so

00:09:14.680 --> 00:09:18.870
for 13 years we tithed regularly,

00:09:18.880 --> 00:09:21.230
and it

00:09:21.240 --> 00:09:23.389
changed our

00:09:23.389 --> 00:09:23.399
lives.

00:09:23.399 --> 00:09:25.389
If I didn't

00:09:25.399 --> 00:09:27.350
learn anything else there, I learned to

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:30.790
tithe.

00:09:39.959 --> 00:09:44.110
When you give God that ten

00:09:44.110 --> 00:09:44.120
percent,

00:09:44.120 --> 00:09:47.509
and that offering above it, I've learned

00:09:47.519 --> 00:09:51.550
that it is a supernatural covenant.

00:09:51.550 --> 00:09:51.560
It's

00:09:51.560 --> 00:09:55.069
a transfer of saying, 'God, I trust

00:09:55.079 --> 00:09:57.790
you with my

00:09:57.800 --> 00:10:00.230
finances

00:10:02.350 --> 00:10:02.360
and

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:07.790
my

00:10:09.310 --> 00:10:09.320
life.'I

00:10:11.440 --> 00:10:13.389
want

00:10:13.399 --> 00:10:15.030
his perfect will

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:20.870
for me and my

00:10:20.870 --> 00:10:20.880
family.

00:10:20.880 --> 00:10:23.430
I've rambled

00:10:23.440 --> 00:10:25.590
on enough, but I wanted to tell

00:10:25.600 --> 00:10:28.710
you all to be watchful of your

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:30.910
surroundings

00:10:30.910 --> 00:10:30.920
and

00:10:30.920 --> 00:10:34.790
listen

00:10:34.800 --> 00:10:37.470
to him, praying a

00:10:37.480 --> 00:10:39.870
hedge of protection over you and your

00:10:39.880 --> 00:10:42.430
children. I'm going to take you

00:10:42.440 --> 00:10:45.310
now to this other video

00:10:45.310 --> 00:10:45.320
where

00:10:45.320 --> 00:10:47.990
you'll see me driving around,

00:10:47.990 --> 00:10:48.000
showing

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:50.590
how I would pray over schools

00:10:50.590 --> 00:10:50.600
and

00:10:50.600 --> 00:10:52.910
churches.

00:10:52.920 --> 00:10:54.870
It's an older

00:10:54.880 --> 00:10:57.590
video, but the message

00:10:57.600 --> 00:10:59.629
is still powerful.

00:10:59.639 --> 00:11:01.509
God bless you

00:11:01.519 --> 00:11:03.190
all.

00:11:03.200 --> 00:11:06.310
Hey, good morning everybody.

00:11:06.320 --> 00:11:08.230
I'm going to take you to a school. The

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:11.790
Lord spoke to me and told me to tell you

00:11:11.800 --> 00:11:15.350
all to pray for your kids.

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:17.350
We're coming into a very dark

00:11:17.360 --> 00:11:20.110
season, and while there's going to be

00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:21.949
light and

00:11:21.959 --> 00:11:23.870
revival,

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:30.590
you can either focus on the darkness or

00:11:30.600 --> 00:11:32.509
the light.

00:11:32.519 --> 00:11:34.629
If I were putting my

00:11:34.639 --> 00:11:36.910
kids in public school, this is what I

00:11:36.920 --> 00:11:39.430
would do.

00:11:39.440 --> 00:11:41.870
I homeschool

00:11:41.880 --> 00:11:44.670
our children; they do BJU,

00:11:44.670 --> 00:11:44.680
which

00:11:44.680 --> 00:11:50.350
is an amazing

00:11:50.350 --> 00:11:50.360
Christian

00:11:50.360 --> 00:11:52.949
homeschool program.

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:01.069
We're going to film

00:12:04.440 --> 00:12:06.230
the school now. If my

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:07.670
little boy or girl were going

00:12:07.680 --> 00:12:10.750
to school, I would drive around

00:12:10.750 --> 00:12:10.760
the

00:12:10.760 --> 00:12:12.949
school

00:12:12.949 --> 00:12:12.959
and

00:12:12.959 --> 00:12:15.509
say, 'Father, I just cover

00:12:15.519 --> 00:12:18.030
this school in the blood of Jesus. I

00:12:18.040 --> 00:12:20.710
thank you that no weapon formed

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:23.590
against this school will

00:12:23.590 --> 00:12:23.600
prosper.'I'm

00:12:23.600 --> 00:12:25.110
going to drive around

00:12:29.720 --> 00:12:31.350
the block where the

00:12:31.360 --> 00:12:33.470
school is. Father, we cover the school

00:12:33.470 --> 00:12:33.480
and the teachers

00:12:33.480 --> 00:12:35.389
in the blood.

00:12:42.800 --> 00:12:45.310
If there are any plots

00:12:45.320 --> 00:12:46.910
or any kind of

00:12:46.910 --> 00:12:46.920
witchcraft

00:12:46.920 --> 00:12:48.750
trying to come against them,

00:12:52.959 --> 00:12:55.389
we

00:12:55.399 --> 00:12:58.269
bind the demonic maneuvering of the

00:12:58.279 --> 00:13:00.310
spirits that would try

00:13:00.320 --> 00:13:03.189
to hurt my children. I

00:13:03.199 --> 00:13:05.389
plead the blood of Jesus over them right

00:13:05.399 --> 00:13:06.990
now. I would sit

00:13:07.000 --> 00:13:08.990
in the parking lot and

00:13:08.990 --> 00:13:09.000
say,

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:10.870
'I send

00:13:10.880 --> 00:13:12.829
my angels out from the north, south,

00:13:12.839 --> 00:13:14.629
east, and west over this school,

00:13:19.519 --> 00:13:21.310
and I thank you, Lord, that your

00:13:21.320 --> 00:13:23.750
angels are protecting

00:13:23.750 --> 00:13:23.760
them.'I

00:13:23.760 --> 00:13:26.350
thank you

00:13:26.360 --> 00:13:29.509
that they are the salt

00:13:29.509 --> 00:13:29.519
and

00:13:29.519 --> 00:13:31.870
the light in this school, and that

00:13:31.880 --> 00:13:34.750
they excel above every other

00:13:34.760 --> 00:13:37.389
student.

00:13:37.399 --> 00:13:40.310
I thank you that my child has

00:13:40.320 --> 00:13:43.829
A's and is on the A-B honor roll. I pray over

00:13:43.839 --> 00:13:46.230
their minds that they would excel and

00:13:46.240 --> 00:13:48.269
have more knowledge. I thank

00:13:48.279 --> 00:13:50.910
you, Lord,

00:13:50.910 --> 00:13:50.920
for

00:13:50.920 --> 00:13:52.910
the

00:13:52.920 --> 00:13:55.670
anointing on them to prosper. I

00:14:05.240 --> 00:14:07.150
put a

00:14:07.160 --> 00:14:09.030
bloodline around this school

00:14:09.030 --> 00:14:09.040
and

00:14:09.040 --> 00:14:11.069
thank you

00:14:11.069 --> 00:14:11.079
for

00:14:11.079 --> 00:14:12.790
the teachers. I thank you

00:14:18.759 --> 00:14:20.629
that you put my child in a good

00:14:20.639 --> 00:14:22.389
classroom

00:14:22.389 --> 00:14:22.399
where

00:14:22.399 --> 00:14:25.189
they're not being taught ungodly things.

